com.koloboke.function
Interface ObjFloatToFloatFunction<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the first argument to the function
public interface ObjFloatToFloatFunction<T>

Represents a function that accepts an object-valued and a float-valued argument and produces a float-valued result. This is the (reference, float, float) specialization of BiFunction.

See Also:
BiFunction
